==Description==
</div>
{{Blurimage|caption=The only image of Foggy Skyscrapers in daytime.|file=Level Skyscraper Daytime.jpg|align=right}}
In daytime, no documentation at this level has been recorded as there was only one record of entering the daytime phase at this level. Such record was added as an entry, which gave some possible clues about how this level behaves.

====Wandering in Daytime====
=====Phenomenon: Reflection Probes=====
During daytime, this level emits small particles with a glistening color and tetrahedral shape into the atmosphere, which refract the sunlight from the sky into various colors. While the level seems to be an open space, lights emitted from an unknown light source seem to slightly affect the color of the sky, which in turn might be evidence showing that the sky at this level has a shape and could possibly be solid in nature. Besides, the wanderer who visited the city during daytime also recorded distortion of shadows and light reflection from windows outside skyscrapers. Some windows reflect the street view of another street while others reflect only the sky, with only a few resembling the true street view in front of the specific window. It is believed that the reflection is determined by a certain "probe" which controls the behavior of reflective objects.


